text: Frozen Assets is a 1992 American comedy movie directed by George T. Miller and starring Shelley Long, Corbin Bernsen, Larry Miller, Dody Goodman, Matt Clark. It was distributed by RKO Radio Pictures and was a box office bomb. ==Other websites== * Category:1992 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by George T.
